---
title: Burrata, Parmigiano and Parma Ham Filled Pasta with Veggie 'Nduja Sauce and Rocket
description: Featuring a hot, umami blend of Calabrian chillies and peppers, this 'Nduja is completely meat-free but with all the same flavour. It pairs perfectly with the creamy filling of our Parmigiano Reggiano and Parma ham filled pasta.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R11_W46_UK_QR21416-9_Main_low-8b854261.jpg
